name: WhoSetMeUp?

And best of all, it’s FREE for everyone.

Lets face it: everyone wants to be SetUp and everyone likes setting people up. WhoSetMeUp? is a social application that lets users anonymously introduce two people who can then communicate with each other using incognito email addresses.

WhoSetMeUp? marries the trustworthiness of a friend’s introduction with the safety of concealed communication so that users can get comfortable with each other before they share their personal information.
